data.title: In pics: city view of Malabo, Equatorial Guinea
data.meta_description: In pics: city view of Malabo, Equatorial Guinea-
data.text:
This photo taken on May 20, 2024 shows the courthouse in Malabo, Equatorial Guinea. Malabo is situated in the northern part of Bioko Island. The city serves as the political, commercial, financial, and cultural hub of Equatorial Guinea. It is also a major aviation hub and an important seaport of the country. (Xinhua/Han Xu)
